    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, top, tail, peel and chop your <strong>carrots</strong> into small, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and grate (or finely chop) your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and grate (or finely chop) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Tip: Take the meat-free mince off the heat if you need longer to chop to avoid burning!</p>",
