    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[450ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [600ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> to the pan and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 10-12 min or until the rice is cooked and the water has been absorbed</p><p>Check and stir occasionally to prevent the rice from sticking to the bottom</p><p>Tip: Add a splash of water if the rice looks a little dry!</p>",
      "order": 6,
