      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>meat-free</strong> <strong>mince</strong> <strong>keema</strong> in bowls</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>reserved coriander leaves </strong>and a <strong>lime wedge </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
